<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>{{title}}</title>
    <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@400;600&display=swap');

      body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        background-color: #f4f4f4;
        font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
        color: #333;
        text-align: center;
      }

      .container {
        max-width: 600px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 20px;
        background-color: #ffffff;
        border-radius: 8px;
        box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 24px;
        color: #4CAF50;
        margin-bottom: 10px;
      }

      p {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 10px 0;
      }

      .info {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        padding: 15px;
        margin: 20px 0;
        border-left: 4px solid #4CAF50;
        text-align: left;
        border-radius: 4px;
      }

      .info p {
        margin: 8px 0;
        font-size: 15px;
      }

      a {
        color: #4CAF50;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 600;
      }

      footer {
        margin-top: 30px;
        font-size: 14px;
        color: #999;
      }

      footer h2 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 16px;
        color: #4CAF50;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>New Contact Form Submission</h1>

      <p>Hi, youâ€™ve received a new message from your website:</p>

      <div class="info">
        <p><strong>First Name:</strong> {{firstName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Last Name:</strong> {{lastName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Email:</strong> <a href="mailto:{{email}}">{{email}}</a></p>
        <p><strong>Phone Number:</strong> {{phoneNumber}}</p>
        <p><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</p>
        <p><strong>Business Name:</strong> {{businessName}}</p>
        <p><strong>Project Type:</strong> {{projectType}}</p>
        <p><strong>Message:</strong><br />{{message}}</p>
      </div>

      <p>Be sure to follow up promptly to keep things moving!</p>

      <footer>
        <h2>{{businessName}}</h2>
        <a target="_blank" rel="noreferrer" href="{{businessUrl}}">{{businessUrl}}</a>
        <p>&copy; {{year}} {{businessName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
